7.Given a number n find the prime factorization of the number.
Platform : GeeksForGeeks 
SOURCE CODE : class Solution {
    public static void printPrimeFactorization(int n) {
       
        for (int i = 2; i * i <= n; i++) {
            while (n % i == 0) {
                System.out.print(i + " ");
                n /= i;
            }
        }

        if (n > 1) {
            System.out.print(n);
        }
    }
}
